sentences.sContent: On the molecular level becoming a kind of maize inbred line, finding a certain similarity on the campestral agronomic characters.

sentences.sContent: Yet despite this inequity and partially because of it, a larger degree of the indigenous peoples retained their campestral culture, wisdom and knowledge.

sentences.sCn: 尽管这不公义的部分原因是因此而起，仍有相当程度的土著人民维持著他们乡野的文化、智慧与知识。
